txt.en: 'The first ingredient I need is several sturdy oak branches recently fallen. You can likely find several in the forest to the west of here.'
Bring the oak branches to Enit at Galar Culch
'You have the oak branches? Very well, leave them with me and find the rest of the things I have asked of you.'

Rituals of the Forest - Oaken Limbs
Enit has asked you to retrieve several strong oaken branches as part of a ritual to summon one of the spirits of the forest.
The oak branches Enit has requested can be gathered in the northern stretches of the Mournshaws.
Bring the oak branches to Enit at Galar Culch
Enit is at Galar Culch in the Mournshaws.\n\nYou should bring the oak branches you have collected to Enit.
